                                                <div class="mb-1 received-message-content border rounded-2 p-3">
                                                    <p class="mb-0">A tree-toad loved a she-toad who lived up in a tree.
                                                        He was a two-toed tree-toad, but a three-toed toad was she. The
                                                        two-toed tree-toad tried to win the three-toed she-toad’s heart, for
                                                        the two-toed tree-toad loved the ground that the three-toed
                                                        tree-toad trod. But the two-toed tree-toad tried in vain; he
                                                        couldn’t please her whim. From her tree-toad bower, with her
                                                        three-toed power, the she-toad vetoed him.</p>
